diary.story: Today I borrowed a pencil from a lost sheep near the broken fence. The battle was confusing. It ended in a strategic retreat. The audience cringed audibly. My trusty Battered Champion's Cape of Basic Training proved essential.

[Auto] Today I unified all combat styles to transcend the source of all violence at the nexus of all warrior spirits. The battle was transcendently powerful. It ended in becoming one with the legend. This battle is now taught in celestial academies. I couldn't have done it without my Astral War-Banner of Shattered Armies.

Today I shattered the morale of a legendary beast at the nexus of power. The battle was fabled. It ended in a title being bestowed. The crowd erupted in cheers. The Warrior's Greaves of Rising Courage glowed with approval.

Today I became the living embodiment of wisdom from the cosmic library of all knowledge in a reality made entirely of information. The research was all-knowing. It ended in reality itself being understood. The cosmic consciousness took notes. I consulted my Apotheosis Scholar's Hat of Omniscient Insight for guidance.

Today I became one with universal truth regarding the origin of all knowledge at the primordial source of wisdom. The research was origin-of-thought. It ended in knowledge itself bowing in respect. Understanding achieved its final form. I consulted my Worn-out Spear of Forgotten Skirmishes for guidance.
